room_title: Escape room "Rob the Mob!" by Escape Game Coeur d'Alene in Coeur d'Alene
room_description: “Scarface” Al Capone and his mob just shoved a tommy gun in your face demanding their weekly cut of your business profits…or else. But those thugs can’t push YOU around! Tonight, you’re going to blast open Capone’s cash safe and steal back what’s rightfully yours. You have one hour before the mob gathers for their poker game, so get in and out quickly! You’ll be sleeping with the fishes if they find you.
